Uses of Package
com.nerjal.json.elements

  • Packages that use com.nerjal.json.elements 
    Package Description
    com.nerjal.json
    This package provides the ability to instantiate and manipulate JSON structures within Java.
    com.nerjal.json.elements
    This package provides all the tools to build and manipulate JSON structures within Java.
    com.nerjal.json.mapper  
    com.nerjal.json.mapper.errors  
    com.nerjal.json.parser
    This package provides all the required tools to properly parse any string or file to JSON and vice-versa.
  • Classes in com.nerjal.json.elements used by com.nerjal.json 
    Class and Description
    JsonElement
    This is the base class for all possible JSON element in this API.
  • Classes in com.nerjal.json.elements used by com.nerjal.json.elements 
    Class and Description
    JsonArray
    An object that lists JSON values, allowing to build arrays for a JSON structure.
    JsonComment
    Represents a JSON comment, inside a JSON structure.
    JsonElement
    This is the base class for all possible JSON element in this API.
    JsonNumber
    A JsonElement allowing instantiation of numbers inside a JSON structure.
    JsonObject
    An object that maps keys to JSON values, allowing to build objects for a JSON structure.
    JsonObject.JsonNode
    A JsonObject entry (key-value pair).
    The JsonObject.entrySet() returns a collection-view of the object, whose values are non comments.
    JsonString
    An object made to symbolise a String in a JSON Structure.
